Lumpy skin disease, Bulgaria
----------------------------
Information received on [and dated] 14 Apr 2016 from Dr Damyan Iliev, Chief Veterinary Officer and Deputy Executive Director, Bulgarian Food Safety Agency, Ministry of Agriculture and Food, Sofia, Bulgaria

Summary
Report type: immediate notification
Date of start of the event: 12 Apr 2016
Date of confirmation of the event: 13 Apr 2016
Reason for notification: 1st occurrence of a listed disease
Causal agent: Lumpy skin disease virus
Nature of diagnosis: laboratory (basic)
This event pertains to a defined zone within the country

New outbreaks (3)
Outbreak 1: Voden, Haskovo, Haskovo
Date of start of the outbreak: 12 Apr 2016
Outbreak status: continuing (or date resolved not provided)
Epidemiological unit: village
